Gitter (Unofficial)
-------------------

Gitter is home to over 25,000 developer communities. The free public
service allows unlimited users, unlimited history and unlimited
integrations.

For native clients for several platforms, including Linux, see
https://gitter.im/#apps-panel
For instruction on their IRC bridge see https://irc.gitter.im/

This web app is not affiliated with Gitter. The Gitter name,
associated trade marks and the Gitter logo are trade marks of Gitter
or related entities.

